{
  "_doc": [
    "Biome + tile registry consumed by scripts/worldgen/biome_classifier.gd and chunk_renderer.gd.",
    "TILES: id -> { colors: [hexA, hexB] (dither pair), walkable, water, hazard }.",
    "BIOMES: classifier picks the highest-priority biome whose 'when' ranges all",
    "match the tile's height/moisture/temp (each 0..1; absent bound = unbounded).",
    "Always keep one biome with priority 0 and empty 'when' as the fallback.",
    "tiles: weighted ground palette. tint: ambient CanvasModulate hex. music: tag",
    "emitted on EventBus.biome_changed. skillWeights: relative chance per gather",
    "skill when populating sites. siteDensity/monsterDensity: spawns per chunk",
    "scale. To add a biome: append an entry here, add zone words in",
    "zone_names.json, and (optionally) reference it from skill_sites.json /",
    "monsters.json / pois.json. No generator code changes needed."
  ],
  "tiles": {
